//把spring boot自动初始化DataSource相关的代码禁止掉
@SpringBootApplication(exclude = { DataSourceAutoConfiguration.class, DataSourceTransactionManagerAutoConfiguration.class })


启动配置说明
@SpringBootApplication  //把spring boot自动初始化DataSource相关的代码禁止掉
//@SpringBootApplication(exclude = { DataSourceAutoConfiguration.class, DataSourceTransactionManagerAutoConfiguration.class })
//@SpringBootApplication(exclude = DataSourceAutoConfiguration.class)
问题  If you want an embedded database (H2, HSQL or Derby), please put it on the classpath.
	If you have database settings to be loaded from a particular profile you may need to activate it (no profiles are currently active)
也可以不配置   p配置类没配置数据源就用@SpringBootApplication(exclude = DataSourceAutoConfiguration.class)

//@PropertySource({ "classpath:quthor.properties"})
@MapperScan({"com.demomodel.mysqlcontroller.mapper"}) //扫描mapper注解  
//扫描包
//@ComponentScan(basePackages = {"com"})  //多个可以用，分割
@EnableAutoConfiguration(exclude={DataSourceAutoConfiguration.class})
@ServletComponentScan   //启动器启动时，扫描本目录以及子目录带有的webservlet注解的  
//@EnableScheduling //开启定时任务
//@ImportResource({"classpath:some-context.xml","classpath:another-context.xml"}) //支持整合xml